    <item>
      <title>JDBC DataSource Configuration in Tomcat</title>
      <link>http://sivalabs.github.io/post/2009/jdbc-datasource-configuration-in-tomcat/</link>
      <pubDate>Tue, 10 Feb 2009 15:03:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>http://sivalabs.github.io/post/2009/jdbc-datasource-configuration-in-tomcat/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;Put a file named context.xml in META-INF folder which contains:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;?xml version=&amp;ldquo;1.0&amp;rdquo; encoding=&amp;ldquo;UTF-8&amp;rdquo;?&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;Context&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;Resource      name=&#34;MySQLDS&#34;     
type=&#34;javax.sql.DataSource&#34;   
driverClassName=&#34;com.mysql.jdbc.Driver&#34;   
password=&#34;root&#34;    
maxIdle=&#34;2&#34;   
maxWait=&#34;5000&#34;    
username=&#34;root&#34;    
url=&#34;jdbc:mysql://localhost:3306/test&#34;     
maxActive=&#34;10&#34;/&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/Context&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Getting the DataSource:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Context context = new InitialContext();&lt;br /&gt;
DataSource MYSQL_DATASOURCE = (DataSource) context.lookup(&amp;ldquo;java:comp/env/MySQLDS&amp;rdquo;);&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
